{"tid":2360830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"手足：車場油漆蓋不住思念","createTime":"2021-01-10T06:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T08:36:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4c91f3ca6bfa9baa1f9176c9f71d134172607349","tid":2360830,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/WH4OJNTIR5HQ3EXQ7BCG2A3ADA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FWH4OJNTIR5HQ3EXQ7BCG2A3ADA%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=3ee43702\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FWH4OJNTIR5HQ3EXQ7BCG2A3ADA%2F&h=a163b6c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/WH4OJNTIR5HQ3EXQ7BCG2A3ADA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n手足：車場油漆蓋不住思念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/y57zAtEoQfDYp6UqY5BbGmoLKuA=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/INE33IDHN5DMNLR452GWUXAPEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fy57zAtEoQfDYp6UqY5BbGmoLKuA%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FINE33IDHN5DMNLR452GWUXAPEU.jpg&h=7a4800c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■年近八旬的李伯經過，當着警察面前向祭壇位置三鞠躬。江子堯攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。有街坊得知裁決結果後，到場為梓樂點蠟燭，即被警方截查並票控亂拋垃圾，她坦言對裁決「唔服」，很多疑團未解開。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：祭壇守護者打游擊悼念<br />\n<br />\n昨晚裁決有結果後僅一小時，開始有大隊警員陸續抵達「尚十祭壇」外戒備，又進入停車場內巡邏，至晚上約9時大隊PTU到場增援，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民點蠟燭悼念遭票控<br />\n<br />\n對於死因研訊結果，因點蠟燭被票控亂拋垃圾的街坊陳小姐坦言「唔服」，很多疑團無法解釋：「唔相信，點解咁重要嘅閉路電視竟然拍唔到？明明得一道門走，就喺嗰道門拍唔到？」亦有街坊緊貼研訊內容，同樣認為不少疑團仍未解開，指梓樂到底是意外還是被殺仍是個謎，目前的結果只是一個段落，給梓樂家人交代。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：有緣街坊首響應呼籲出庭  是證人也是守護者「悲劇中找些好事」<br />\n<br />\n至於尚德停車場內，梓樂墮下的二、三樓石壆位，大半年前已被領展用白布圍封。領展回應指改善工程早於2018年展開，至去年3月起擴展到該場區做翻新油漆工程，同時進行閉路電視改善工程，及於適當位置重鋪防滑設施。雖然有關梓樂的痕迹被牆壁上的白油蓋過，昔日掛滿紙鶴、遍地燭光花海不再，但細心看圍封的白布上有人留下「愛您」二字，石壆上仍留有一個「念」字。<br />\n<br />\n尚德十字路口祭壇位置已圍上鐵板，。。。。。。。。。。」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警禁留守 伯伯堅持鞠躬<br />\n<br />\n每到夜幕低垂，尚十祭壇總會出現幾名警察展開長夜監視。路過的市民都不敢多作停留，惟年近八旬的李伯買餸經過，在警察面前向祭壇位置三鞠躬，更說：「我特登喺佢面前拜嘅，驚佢做咩呀，唔好驚佢。」居住尚德邨20多年的李伯過去每晚守候花壇，直至警方以限聚為由禁止聚集，他便不再留守，他負擔不起買花的錢，惟每次經過看到有花，便會肅立鞠躬致意：「有花即係有人紀念佢、拜祭佢，咁我又參加拜祭&hellip;&hellip;我尊敬佢，佢係為正義犧牲咗。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dlxzXDzA24jJR78CUnoWqVeR2d0=/1536x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5BOAU3FI4VFAVGXIRZAEFAT5JA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdlxzXDzA24jJR78CUnoWqVeR2d0%3D%2F1536x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5BOAU3FI4VFAVGXIRZAEFAT5JA.jpg&h=683e6662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■街坊陳小姐昨晚獨自到停車場前點蠟燭，遭便衣警截停及票控亂拋垃圾。"},{"pid":"5c5ed1188c73ca4de8369482ed033f10eab9fd0d","tid":2360830,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df0328b4f33823a3c9636081320ade364adecf0","tid":2360830,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse